Limitations of CRM Analytics on Android Devices:

General Limitations:
- Landscape mode is supported only for tablets.
- Portrait mode is supported for both tablets and phones.
- Split screen isn’t supported.
- Can't create, edit or delete sharing permissions.
- Can't save or clone lenses.
- Can't delete datasets or lenses from mobile device.
- Can't import data to mobile device.
- Local playground data isn’t supported.
- Favorites are stored locally on mobile device and aren’t synced.

Data Exploration and Visualization Limitations:
- Charts don’t support multiple selection actions such as copy and focus.
- Pivot tables aren’t supported.
- Sankey charts aren’t supported.
- Rating charts aren’t supported.
- Image widget doesn’t support .svg files.
- Number widget isn't supported for exploring.
- Queries have varying results limits based on type.
- Apex steps (beta) aren’t supported on mobile.
- Dashboards designed in CRM Analytics Studio may appear different on mobile.
title: Limitations of CRM Analytics on Android Devices
